ull h-[2px] bg-primary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500\"></span></a><a class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors relative group py-2\" href=\"/vision\">Our Vision<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-primary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500\"></span></a><a class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors relative group py-2\" href=\"/network\">Connect<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-primary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500\"></span></a><a class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors relative group py-2\" href=\"/news\">Latest News<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-primary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500\"></span></a><a class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors relative group py-2\" href=\"/events\">Events<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-primary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500\"></span></a><div><a class=\"border-2 border-zinc-200 text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all active:scale-95\" href=\"/signup\">Sign Up</a></div><div><a class=\"bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(255,0,51,0.3)] active:scale-95\" href=\"/login\">Login</a></div></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 bg-zinc-100 rounded-xl\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></nav></div><main class=\"min-h-screen pt-20\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white pt-32 pb-20\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-30\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(to bottom, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:80px 80px;mask-image:radial-gradient(400px circle at 0px 0px, black, transparent);-webkit-mask-image:radial-gradient(400px circle at 0px 0px, black, transparent)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #f4f4f5 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(to bottom, #f4f4f5 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:80px 80px\"></div></div><div class=\"section-padding relative z-10\"><div class=\"mb-12\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/events\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg> Back to Events</a></div><div class=\"max-w-4xl mb-32\"><span class=\"text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4 block\">Major Event</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-9xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-8 italic text-black uppercase leading-[0.9]\">ANNUAL SUMMIT <br/><span class=\"text-primary not-italic\">2026.</span></h1><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-6 md:p-10 py-10 border-y-2 border-zinc-100 my-12\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest\">Date</p><p class=\"font-bold\">August 15-17, 2026</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest\">Location</p><p class=\"font-bold\">Istanbul, Turkey</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg><div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest\">Attendance</p><p class=\"font-bold\">500+ Alumni</p></div></div></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-medium\">Join hundreds of graduates from all generations for our biggest event of the year. The 2026 Summit focuses on &quot;Global Impact &amp; Leadership&quot; - helping you take your career to the next level while staying connected to your roots.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:p-20 mb-40\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-20\"><div class=\"space-y-10\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold uppercase italic\">The <span class=\"text-primary not-italic\">Agenda.</span></h2><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 group\"><div class=\"text-primary font-mono font-bold text-xl pt-1\">09:00</div><div class=\"flex-1 pb-10 border-b border-zinc-100 space-y-3\"><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Opening Ceremony</h4><p class=\"text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed\">Welcome address from the organization leaders.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 group\"><div class=\"text-primary font-mono font-bold text-xl pt-1\">11:00</div><div class=\"flex-1 pb-10 border-b border-zinc-100 space-y-3\"><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Professional Networking</h4><p class=\"text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed\">Meet fellow graduates in your industry.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 group\"><div class=\"text-primary font-mono font-bold text-xl pt-1\">14:00</div><div class=\"flex-1 pb-10 border-b border-zinc-100 space-y-3\"><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Innovation Workshops</h4><p class=\"text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed\">Deep dive into future technology and career growth.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 group\"><div class=\"text-primary font-mono font-bold text-xl pt-1\">19:00</div><div class=\"flex-1 pb-10 border-b border-zinc-100 space-y-3\"><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Alumni Dinner</h4><p class=\"text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed\">A formal dinner celebrating our shared achievements.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-50 rounded-[40px] p-6 md:p-12 sticky top-8 md:p-32 space-y-12 border-2 border-zinc-100\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 uppercase\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg> Registration Info</h3><p class=\"text-muted font-medium mb-8\">Early bird tickets are available until May 1st. Includes access to all workshops, formal dinner, and networking sessions.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-between font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-zinc-200 pb-4\"><span class=\"text-muted\">Standard Ticket</span><span>$150 USD</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-zinc-200 pb-4\"><span class=\"text-muted\">Early Bird (-20%)</span><span class=\"text-primary\">$120 USD</span></div></div><div><button class=\"w-full bg-primary text-white py-6 rounded-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-2xl\">Secure Regular Spot</button></div><p class=\"text-[10px] text-center font-bold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest\">Financial aid is available for recent graduates.</p></div></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-white pt-32 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-zinc-100\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-[300px] 